Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.73,0:00:03.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Wednesday Downtown,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.17,0:00:09.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's get on with our first presenter please
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.71,0:00:18.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please welcome FUJIWARA!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:23.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hello everyone, we are comedians  \N-Welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.05,0:00:25.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We are a comedian combo, thanks for having us  \N-It's a combo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.15,0:00:30.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time we bring you the second instance of a five-year-old theory
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.28,0:00:32.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The theory is this:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.28,0:00:37.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The 2nd "You won't realize something is your own possession if its in the hands of someone else"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.78,0:00:38.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:42.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It has been done before
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.03,0:00:45.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are many copycats of this theory on youtube \N-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.96,0:00:47.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, quite a few
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.80,0:00:49.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Must have good reviews
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.37,0:00:52.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then its possible that our program is the one copying it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.10,0:00:54.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Possibly, possibly, this program could do such a thing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:00:56.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No one will find out if we copy something anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.07,0:00:58.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So then,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.08,0:01:02.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Will the subject notice the items have been taken out of their house?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.81,0:01:03.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.84,0:01:05.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.32,0:01:12.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Verify that all comedians have their own "Asakusa Kid"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.58,0:01:35.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Once again, we will verify whether or not people can tell items are theirs when they are in the hands of others
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.13,0:01:39.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, with the assistance of their managers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.50,0:01:42.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The personal belongings of the subject are taken from their home
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.15,0:01:47.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And presented to them in different scenarios
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.74,0:01:48.32,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Semi-thief behavior now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.95,0:01:51.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The first target is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.36,0:01:55.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Morita
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.07,0:01:58.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Good morning
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.33,0:02:02.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Fake meetings are set up to test the targets
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.54,0:02:06.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The first items are set up in this cafe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.83,0:02:11.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Recently, Morita moved into this 2LDK apartment
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.09,0:02:18.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In the living room is a poster of Muhammad Ali
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.64,0:02:18.72,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just saw it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:21.54,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seems easy to spot
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.01,0:02:24.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,However, it was hard to notice because it was behind him
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.73,0:02:29.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,During conversation, the topic of interior decoration comes up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.36,0:02:30.43,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The poster seems to match this cafe's style
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:37.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A framed photo ... I did buy one
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.22,0:02:37.48,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah he's spotted it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.48,0:02:38.99,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He's noticed it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.04,0:02:43.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, this one
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:45.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.19,0:02:45.81,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You don't think it's your own, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.28,0:02:47.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's this one
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.38,0:02:50.19,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is  \N-Just seems like a coincidence
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.82,0:02:50.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I recently bought this one
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.79,0:02:52.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ali?  \N-I recently bought it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:54.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, this one of Ali
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.72,0:02:58.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Mine is probably a little bigger
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:02:57.63,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, no, it's the same it's the same
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.06,0:03:02.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Bigger than this one?  \N-Bigger than this
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.63,0:03:00.24,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Shameful \N-Feels different in different spaces, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:03.24,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah, at home it seems bigger
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:04.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Muhammad Ali \N-Yeah, this
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:10.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There is obviously no subtle difference in size
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.99,0:03:14.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In short, Morita did not realize the item was his own
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.81,0:03:19.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The next item is a sofa
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.37,0:03:24.13,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's bold!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.75,0:03:29.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm most interested in furniture, especially furniture stores
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.92,0:03:28.28,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's integration into the environment is too good
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.76,0:03:32.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Since I moved place I thought I'd buy a load of new stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.93,0:03:36.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There's sofas and ...  \N-How much did the sofa cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.43,0:03:43.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sofa... uh, I think ah about 400,000
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.31,0:03:47.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's a 400,000 sofa like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.64,0:03:51.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Actually it's nothing special, doesn't look very high grade or anything
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:52.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's a corduroy sofa
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.82,0:03:57.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just like that one over there, pretty much the same
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:03:59.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:02.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is that one corduroy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:04.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's really similar to this
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:07.38,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it just feel like his own home?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:08.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Its not the kind of thing that looks very high grade
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.93,0:04:10.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not very extravagantly made
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.02,0:04:12.38,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hasn't realized it's exactly the same
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:14.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They bought a similar sofa
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.99,0:04:14.38,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Similar
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.54,0:04:21.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Having your home and a new trendy place like this set up the same feels really good
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:22.43,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Didn't realize
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:23.55,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although it looks exactly the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:27.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He fails to think "The items are actually exactly the same"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:34.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After that, he ignores the mannequin placed at the entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:37.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The store owner and I really have the same taste
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:40.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Later on, a fake gourmet report
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:43.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's not too late, let's go in and take a look
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:44.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:47.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.44,0:04:50.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm Morita, thanks very much for having me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:52.56,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,T-shirt...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:55.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It'll get oily, so annoying  \N-It's going to smell
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:57.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And then,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.48,0:05:00.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So you like American casual too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:02.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah, although I don't only wear American casual
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:03.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I also like to buy vintage stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:07.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yeah yeah yeah, I actually have the exact same t-shirt
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:08.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really?  \N-Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:12.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is this vintage?  \N-Yes, it is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:16.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The same, exactly the same, really, probably
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.26,0:05:17.58,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,The fumes are so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:17.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really alike
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.56,0:05:22.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Even so, he still didn't realize it's his own possession
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.02,0:05:26.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, we set an even bolder trap next
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.98,0:05:31.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The pork face and beef tongue is tossed with soy sauce
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:35.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Liver and diaphragm are flavored with miso
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:42.73,special_Wed_1_2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(714,884)}An individual dressed entirely in Morita's clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:38.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Welcome, one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.13,0:05:38.48,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Full body
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:42.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please sit here
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:43.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So they're open for business!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:44.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.63,0:05:50.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's pretty crowded
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:55.51,special_Wed_1_2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,876)}A couple dressed in Morita's clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.42,0:05:53.78,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,A girl too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:05:58.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.31,0:06:00.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Two new customers
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:09.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Morita finally begins to awaken due to an unmistakeable feeling of familiarity
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:12.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,However, after that too
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:12.78,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Still no reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.86,0:06:18.40,special_Wed_1_2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726,876)}More female customers dressed in Morita's clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.98,0:06:16.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Way too many people!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:17.91,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Girls
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.66,0:06:23.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This store is so popular!  \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.43,0:06:28.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, here is your potato salad, please enjoy your meal
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:29.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ok
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:35.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A response so cold that one wouldn't think he was on location for a food review
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.94,0:06:38.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And then,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:43.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Regulars who like American casual...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:46.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So many!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.56,0:06:49.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We all know each other pretty well  \N-Yeah seems like it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.96,0:06:51.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:59.74,special_Wed_1_2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(723,880)}A whole group of guests resembles Morita
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:58.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please sterilize over here. Three of you, right? Please sit here
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.98,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can't take anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:03.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They're all American casual...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.49,0:07:07.22,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's not the point
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.03,0:07:11.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Faced with such an unusual situation, Morita's state no longer reflects that of an on-location shoot
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:20.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Here we add the tenth person
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:23.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,American casual again
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:25.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait, wait, wait, wait
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:28.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Give me a minute. Hey, what the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.01,0:07:27.30,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Realized
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.33,0:07:32.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I have all the same ones, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:36.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thus, the truth is revealed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:43.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is this, seriously!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:46.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, you guys almost got... ah
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.25,0:07:47.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's all mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:50.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They're all wearing my clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.92,0:07:56.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"You won't realize something is your own possession if its in the hands of someone else"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:07:59.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, no... if you say so, I guess
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.46,0:08:02.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I only realized because you did it to this extent
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:03.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Which of these clothes is the most expensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:07.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That, that, that  \N-How much is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:09.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,110,000
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:09.71,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So old and expensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:11.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What did you do before this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:13.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Before coming here?  \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:17.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I had a meeting before coming here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:22.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The Muhammad Ali poster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:25.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah ah ah ah
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.19,0:08:27.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, sofa!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,From my home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:32.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It is indeed unexpectedly difficult to realize
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.98,0:08:34.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But anyway, all of you get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.96,0:08:36.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't suck up the fumes in here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:39.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't let my American casual absorb the smell here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.88,0:08:44.18,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The next target is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:48.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Sakai here
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.77,0:08:51.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Good morning, I'm TBS' announcer Yasumi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:53.16,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Will Sakai realize?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:57.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time the stage is a thrift store
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:09:05.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The store is currently selling a lot of Sakai's personal items
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:04.01,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can he realize?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.01,0:09:05.39,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,After all, there are many items around
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:08.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not long after the shooting started,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.53,0:09:10.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? There's have CUTRATE stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:13.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? Just 100? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:15.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I have the exact same thing \N-The exact same thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:17.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When I bought it it was expensive
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:20.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is even cheaper than in the Philippines
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.05,0:09:21.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:25.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:27.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think I also have this
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:30.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You have this at home too?  \N-Eh? Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.85,0:09:33.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Being faced with a prepared product that is very much to his taste
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:34.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The Switch is so cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:39.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sakai becomes very excited
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:40.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:44.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,All the things I like!  \N-It's great
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:48.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next, in the appliances section,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.80,0:09:52.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sakai's TV and refrigerator have been placed
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:52.23,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Even this is for sale? \N-Impressive
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:55.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This... seems
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.38,0:09:56.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what this is? It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:09:59.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ahhhhh, this is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:02.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:03.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,AQUOS, ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:07.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? It's so cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:11.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I bought it for about 80,000 \N-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:12.66,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Still hasn't realized
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.63,0:10:14.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I should've come here first
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:16.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Should just moved into the store and live here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.27,0:10:22.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Actually, Sakai just moved from his hometown in December of last year
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.11,0:10:23.29,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,King of Conte
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.07,0:10:28.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time, we took advantage of his absence and removed all of the belongings
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.34,0:10:29.61,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,So messed up
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.61,0:10:31.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A big project!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.87,0:10:37.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And put them up for sale in the various sections of the thrift store
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:39.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wow, there's a bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.06,0:10:42.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:49.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:49.18,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's about time to realize
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:51.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.87,0:10:53.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is too similar
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:57.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is it similar to yours? \N -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:05.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But it's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:08.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's true that it can't be exactly the same  \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:11.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Safe
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:13.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.26,0:11:16.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They also sell teeth \N-Wow so disgusting
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.73,0:11:17.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.66,0:11:20.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.31,0:11:24.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although this item seems unexplainable
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.54,0:11:30.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,These are actually Sakai's baby teeth from his home
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:32.54,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Baby teeth?  \N-Who the hell knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.78,0:11:33.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who would be impressed by this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:37.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Teeth
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.41,0:11:38.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I want these teeth
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:40.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's someones personal belonging, right? \N -Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:43.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You want to buy the teeth?  \N-I want it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:48.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Unbelievably, he buys it without realizing it's his own teeth
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.67,0:11:50.77,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He won't realize? \N-So interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:52.06,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This must be a global first
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:53.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Purchasing your own milk teeth
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.26,0:11:56.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Lastly, the clothing area
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.82,0:12:04.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,About half of the clothes hanging on the shelves here belong to Sakai
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:04.82,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Surely he'll realize now
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:06.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wow, so stylish!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.51,0:12:08.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:12.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is it?  \N-Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.28,0:12:14.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.07,0:12:17.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Am I at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.82,0:12:19.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Sakai?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.59,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You can't be at home
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.02,0:12:21.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:24.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why do I have the impression that I have all of these?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:25.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Gross...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:29.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I bought this for, like, 60,000
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:31.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But it can't be the exact same thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.74,0:12:40.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The size is also the same \N-The size is appropriate?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:44.23,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He pulled something out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.35,0:12:48.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Red LARK, that's what I smoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:51.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Even the cigarettes are the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.22,0:12:51.89,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why'd you put it in the pocket anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.42,0:12:54.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is too much of a coincidence
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.42,0:12:57.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It seems that you and the previous owner have the same interests
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:12:59.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This kind of thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:03.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Even the cigarettes you smoke are the same, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:07.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Can such a thing happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:10.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Unfinished cigarettes in the pocket?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:14.41,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Actually took it out
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:17.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But I don't think it's possible that it is yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:20.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, indeed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:25.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But... the apartment I moved into has a lot of bad people around
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:28.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You mean someone stole from you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.34,0:13:31.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, it's too gross
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:35.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But isn't it strange that it would be sold here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:41.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sakai realizes he may have been the victim of a crime
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:47.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Finally, we added more significant items
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:49.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:56.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A 20-year-old sweatshirt autographed by Ogura Yuko
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.28,0:13:57.59,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:00.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And then,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.93,0:14:08.01,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,He is particularly fond of Yuko
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:11.85,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's going through his mind
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.85,0:14:12.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:16.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really...really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:18.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.37,0:14:21.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is it, Sakai? Do you like Yuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:23.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:25.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Isn't that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.72,0:14:27.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Good isn't... it's not good
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:29.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:36.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? Why is it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:39.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How much is it?  \N-2400
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:40.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't get it, this is a bit scary... I'll buy this one first
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.53,0:14:44.92,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, this is your own
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:46.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Buy... I bought... I don't get it
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:53.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sakai falls into a state of confusion and begins pacing back and forth
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.03,0:14:56.69,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Scary scary scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:59.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Where is this store located?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:00.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's in Ayase
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.38,0:15:03.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ayase, right? In Adachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:04.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Adachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:07.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.13,0:15:08.94,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Does it matter where you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.69,0:15:10.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No... Adachi....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,0:15:14.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, it's not, how should I... eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:14.47,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not good \N-Don't say what you shouldn't say
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:17.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This kind of thing also happens, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:17.97,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It'd be strange if it did
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.97,0:15:19.48,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is not what businesses in Adachi do
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:22.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so, the imagination begins to flood the brain with negative thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:28.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Just in case, Sakai purchased back all the clothes he could with the cash he had on hand
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.60,0:15:32.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yep, I bought a load of stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.14,0:15:33.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,All of this only cost 9,000
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.92,0:15:35.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.71,0:15:38.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,An hour later...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.26,0:15:44.42,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You couldn't {\i1}not{\i0} be scared \N-Completely empty
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:45.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:47.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.24,0:16:04.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,One hour after the end of the on-location shoot
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.42,0:16:09.48,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You couldn't {\i1}not{\i0} be scared \N-Completely empty
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:10.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.19,0:16:12.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.42,0:16:15.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.47,0:16:17.66,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Scary! \N-Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.86,0:16:18.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:21.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.40,0:16:26.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:29.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:30.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.61,0:16:34.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is my house, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:35.51,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,How would you have gotten in?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:38.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Faced with this radical change,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:43.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sakai doesn't seem to be convinced that this is his place
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:46.99,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thought you were in the wrong house?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.76,0:16:47.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So scary
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:50.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.03,0:16:53.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.73,0:16:57.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Haaah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.85,0:16:59.37,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. Is he okay? \N -Sitting down
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.84,0:17:02.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh? There's nothing left
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.47,0:17:06.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At last, we finally told him the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.47,0:17:12.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Absolutely nothing. Who are you? What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:14.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What is this? How...what the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.28,0:17:17.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is my house, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:18.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This is my house, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.89,0:17:20.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.45,0:17:22.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Maybe not. Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:24.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This should be my home
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.63,0:17:27.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because I used the key to get in
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.16,0:17:28.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:30.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Eh, no way! So gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.70,0:17:33.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is this really the case? Huh? Because just now
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.10,0:17:35.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I thought it was strange
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:38.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I just went to a very strange place
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.63,0:17:39.64,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's not a strange place
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.44,0:17:40.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yuyu Market
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.92,0:17:41.29,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Its not a strange place
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.71,0:17:42.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.78,0:17:45.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, they all took it away?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:47.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The whole place is empty?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.05,0:17:51.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sold it all? Sold to a thrift store?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.79,0:17:54.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Wait, that's weird...then I have to buy it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:57.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, no, that's not the point
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:17:58.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why is your brain wired different to ours?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.63,0:18:01.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I need to buy it back quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:05.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oh but thank god, I thought i'd died
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.37,0:18:06.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You thought you were dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.44,0:18:09.54,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When I was shooting on location, I thought, "Oh, I'm dying"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:14.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I thought I had died and someone was helping me sort through my belongings
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:16.60,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What nonsense are you talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.48,0:18:21.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H3732FF&}In summary\N{\r}you'll think your stuff has been stolen or you hung yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.35,0:18:22.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So that's how it is
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:24.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you all think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.89,0:18:27.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A girl should be able to realize right away, right?  \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:30.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,One's taste and the feel of the clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.66,0:18:33.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Especially when wearing a jacket, the clothes would change according to their body type, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.06,0:18:34.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With this it should be obvious
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.96,0:18:36.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You'd definitely realize \N-Ah really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:38.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sakai is abnormal
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:41.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Generally, you'd think seeing LARK cigarettes would be enough to realize it \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.67,0:18:44.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There are many strange aspects, right? Like buying his own baby teeth
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.34,0:18:46.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It would be understandable if you knew that it was your own milk teeth
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:49.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But he bought it thinking it was someone else's teeth
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:52.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,People don't generally buy other people's teeth, do they
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:53.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What's he gonna do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:56.05,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"I thought I was dead."  \N-"I thought I was dead."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:58.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thought someone was helping him sort out his belongings \N-On the way to the afterlife
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:01.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't have told him the truth and just kept watching
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:04.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How he'll live after having already died
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:09.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Let's welcome the next presenter
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.65,0:19:12.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:18.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please welcome, Football Hour's Goto! \N-Thank you for having me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:20.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Koching" isn't it, "Koching"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.48,0:19:21.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Koching" has arrived
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.78,0:19:23.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What the hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:25.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,First of all, Hitori
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.75,0:19:28.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on "Asakura KID" being a huge hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.75,0:19:28.99,note_Wed - Mid,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}※Film based on Takeshi Kitano's autobiography, released on Netflix last December and topped the popularity charts that week
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.99,0:19:30.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.72,0:19:32.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thank you everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.53,0:19:33.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto-san also watched it  \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.89,0:19:34.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's wonderful
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:37.59,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think it only left out one thing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.59,0:19:40.20,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see the whole thing with the axe
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.59,0:19:42.90,note_Wed - Mid,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}※Last September, Takeshi Kitano's car was attacked by a man with an axe, but fortunately, only the window was broken and the occupants were safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:42.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That would have to be a very long shot
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.90,0:19:44.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How much longer do you want it to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:47.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.11,0:19:48.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's a really outstanding piece of work
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.94,0:19:51.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And there's a song that is featured in the movie
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.43,0:19:54.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Also known as "Asakusa KID"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.98,0:19:58.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And so, this time I bring you a related theory:
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:20:02.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Every comedian has his or her own "Asakusa KID"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.69,0:20:08.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This time, we found a few groups of struggling comedians
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:13.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And encouraged them to compose lyrics pertaining to their current situation
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.49,0:20:16.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To sing their own version of "Asakusa KID"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.10,0:20:17.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:20.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For comedians, especially when they are young, it is common to experience hardships
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.28,0:20:24.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Even Downtown, who quickly became big stars, also suffered, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.73,0:20:27.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.68,0:20:28.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For about four years...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.42,0:20:31.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Three or four years of our lives were not great \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:33.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The period where you can't make enough to live on
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:35.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's right, that's right
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.38,0:20:36.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And having to do part-time jobs on the side
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.12,0:20:39.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Was there a period when you live on borrowed money?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.72,0:20:42.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We had to borrow money from ours seniors and so on \N-Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.81,0:20:44.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We borrowed from Momoko
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:46.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ah, Momoko
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:49.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And Tomiiz helped us find work \N-Ah yes, yes, yes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.98,0:20:51.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I didn't know what I was doing, but I just kept pressing a button
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:53.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Inventory
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.11,0:20:55.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It was probably sending Morse code to North Korea
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.88,0:20:57.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.64,0:20:59.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Now that's working for a living
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.67,0:21:01.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The salary for a job like that should be pretty good
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:02.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Oi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.68,0:21:09.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Verify that all comedians have their own "Asakusa Kid"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.82,0:21:14.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For this theory, we assembled three groups of artists with more than 20 years of experience
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.09,0:21:18.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A group of hilarious entertainers that still can't make a name for themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.48,0:21:20.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Firstly,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.56,0:21:27.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With 25 years of experience: AL-Shalaqani
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.68,0:21:29.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Waiting for a bus next to you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.56,0:21:31.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next sentence next sentence  \N-Pretending to be a clock
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.80,0:21:32.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's not something you can pretend to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:39.48,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Ten years ago, they were finalists in "THE MANZAI" for two consecutive years
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.55,0:21:44.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They had stepped on the ladder to stardom
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.09,0:21:47.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please allow us to make an appearance on stage first
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:50.79,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The work they get as comedians today
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.79,0:21:53.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is just a few stage performances each month
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.23,0:21:57.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you have any work scheduled after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.17,0:21:58.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,There is no more work
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.90,0:22:00.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No more today
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.40,0:22:02.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I should say there is no more after today either
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.64,0:22:04.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We used to have about 20 shows each month
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.67,0:22:07.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Now only 10 left
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.41,0:22:09.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Or maybe less
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.55,0:22:14.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Of course, we don't have any TV work
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.65,0:22:18.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although i'm not sure if it can really be considered income
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:18.56,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What a place to do a close-up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.25,0:22:21.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,About ten or twenty thousand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.12,0:22:22.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In all honesty
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.76,0:22:27.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Mine is about three...four...less than 50,000
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:32.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Formed in 1997
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.28,0:22:35.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Even gonna shoot this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.65,0:22:40.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Looking back, it's clear they've entered the later stage of life
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.28,0:22:42.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Rent is 25,000
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.35,0:22:47.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,For these comedians who only earn tens of thousands of yen each month
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.19,0:22:49.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Life is difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.80,0:22:54.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Seiwa, who is in charge of writing, is already married
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.12,0:22:57.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, to secure a living
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.46,0:23:01.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He acts as a lecturer to earn a meager income
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.49,0:23:04.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Barely getting by
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.87,0:23:10.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If the income could increase then of course i'd be very happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.44,0:23:16.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But if it really worried me I wouldn't be with him in the first place
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.53,0:23:19.38,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really nice wife
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.51,0:23:22.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As long as I work a little harder to fill in the gaps, it is not a problem at all
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:29.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The main source of income for Shiro Aikata is part-time jobs
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.00,0:23:34.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Working at a bathhouse
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.00,0:23:36.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,From about 4:00 am to 8:00 am
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.64,0:23:39.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Three to four days a week
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.70,0:23:44.64,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I make about 60,000 a month from it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.04,0:23:47.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because it is impossible to live like this
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.60,0:23:51.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I also work in a curry restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.86,0:23:54.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Opened by the comedian Makio
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.12,0:23:57.42,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm the store manager of the Shinjuku branch of his curry store
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.29,0:24:01.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A hard-working life
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.42,0:24:05.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I once had to take out a very large loan
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.13,0:24:08.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In total about 12 million  \N-The sum total
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.30,0:24:10.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Total
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.52,0:24:17.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Shiro owes a large amount of a large loan due to his exposure to pyramid schemes during his early days
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.50,0:24:21.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,When the loan had accumulated 4 million in interest
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.87,0:24:24.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I cried and asked my parents to pay it off for me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.85,0:24:27.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Your parents sold a mountain, didn't they?  \N-Yes, they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.48,0:24:32.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,50 years-old and still waiting for their big break
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.64,0:24:36.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although not an impossible task
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.23,0:24:41.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Our lack of progress in the past few years is clear
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.53,0:24:42.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And we're getting on in years
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.01,0:24:46.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What exactly is the reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.89,0:24:51.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And what helps them to persist in a world which offers no guarantees?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.50,0:24:56.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To repay the kindness of those who have taken care of me, I just can't give up
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.41,0:25:00.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We must also repay the kindness to our partner
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.38,0:25:03.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Being finalists in THE MANZAI for two years in a row
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.09,0:25:06.19,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's entirely due to my partner
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.19,0:25:09.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Not having been able to progress any further is my problem
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.29,0:25:16.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think it's because we haven't proven how interesting our style is
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.53,0:25:20.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As long as my partner is still writing performances, I won't give up as a comedian
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.85,0:25:24.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I would like to say "why don't we just quit"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.47,0:25:28.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think giving up before making it is unacceptable
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.92,0:25:32.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,25 years of total dedication to manzai
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.38,0:25:36.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Step by step, they continue toward the future on the road of uncertainty
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.51,0:25:40.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, please enjoy this song by the two members of AL-Shalaqani
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.26,0:25:48.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,0)}That performance where I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.77,0:25:56.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)}A layman named "Shiro"
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.81,0:26:04.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You who were supposed to be the audience
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.15,0:26:11.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You acted like an idiot for me
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.12,0:26:18.99,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In a silent hall in Shinjuku
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.99,0:26:27.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,450)}A performance hall with only nine audience members
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.87,0:26:39.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)}Knights, Audrey and even Ujiko
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.21,0:26:46.22,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Guys of the same generation have all made their mark
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.22,0:26:53.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thought there was no longer a place for us
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.20,0:27:00.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)}As we were overtaken by Nishikigoi
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.80,0:27:08.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Witnessed the reversing success of two fifty-year-olds
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.24,0:27:16.95,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,450)}Although we always held the dream of "Someday"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.19,0:27:20.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I can't keep letting my wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.79,0:27:23.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Work six or seven days a week
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.63,0:27:28.10,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You have to carry the family on your shoulders
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.10,0:27:30.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,This idea is deep-rooted in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.07,0:27:34.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Rent...I'm really sorry for not being able to pay on time
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.97,0:27:36.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I haven't been in touch with you  \N-Don't say that. It's okay
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.90,0:27:40.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'll definitely pay it off when I hit the big time
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.34,0:27:42.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That would be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.15,0:27:50.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't say we aren't young anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.72,0:27:57.49,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That we've never had a taste of fame
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.49,0:28:06.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fadd(0,450)}Don't say we're worn out
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.50,0:28:14.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}That we've never had a taste of fame
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.04,0:28:24.60,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,What...what?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.38,0:28:26.82,wipe_Wed,,0,0,0,,You want to win an award, or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.66,0:28:30.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't particularly want to win an award \N-This show
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.09,0:28:32.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's pretty "eh----"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.33,0:28:38.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The next two artists who couldn't scale the heights of popularity are these two
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.54,0:28:48.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With 29 years of experience, Nichokenju
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.98,0:28:51.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Who's idea was it to perform this segment?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.78,0:28:56.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In recent years, if they've had the opportunity to appear
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.83,0:29:00.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's almost always with one of their wives, Yukiko Nonomura
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.93,0:29:02.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,However, in actual fact
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.83,0:29:10.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The two of them were popular at Osaka's 2-chome theater
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.57,0:29:12.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Super popular \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.57,0:29:13.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Unimaginably
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.60,0:29:18.71,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Iconic and harmonious stars with an overwhelming power to attract support
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.24,0:29:24.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,People say we were fast for our generation
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.55,0:29:27.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"You can't walk without causing a riot in the street," Jinnai used to say
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.45,0:29:33.12,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"That's what popularity is" was commonly said
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.58,0:29:38.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,As long as we were on the performance list, the audience was almost all there to see us
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.72,0:29:42.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So the two rode this momentum all the way to Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.54,0:29:46.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And even appeared once on the stage of the M-1 final
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.35,0:29:50.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They were on track to become household names...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.27,0:29:56.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although they are a year below me, I was really impressed by them
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.25,0:29:59.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's not over the top to say that they were the pillar of the 2-chome theater
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.15,0:30:03.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After all, without them there would be no one to see
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.39,0:30:08.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Thanks to their popularity, our generation is what it is today
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.94,0:30:13.33,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Why didn't the two of them make a splash in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.90,0:30:15.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think its down to pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.80,0:30:19.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"I don't have anymore strength, but I have to keep rushing ahead"
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.04,0:30:23.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The popularity at the time was so high that they were forced forwards
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.74,0:30:27.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Both Yoshimoto and the fans egged them on
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.61,0:30:30.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you enclose that with a circle...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.14,0:30:33.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Now, in terms of their current work
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.91,0:30:38.31,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They have only a handful of stage performances left in a month
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.49,0:30:49.40,special_Wed_1_X,,0,0,0,,{\pos(294,724)\fad(295,0)}Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.92,0:30:43.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How much of their total work currently is comedy?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.23,0:30:49.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Comedy just accounts for about 30 percent
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.26,0:30:53.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kohori is the group's writer
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.82,0:31:00.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,His attitude toward manzai started to change about ten years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.24,0:31:06.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In response to this situation, his partner said
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.05,0:31:14.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kohori said "I'm here to entertain the public, so I need to try many things"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.46,0:31:15.62,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although I understood his feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.62,0:31:18.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,He puts equal effort into all of them
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.83,0:31:22.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Manzai 1, music 1, rakugo 1, like this
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.73,0:31:26.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Manzai 5, music 1, rakugo 1
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.46,0:31:29.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If it was like this then l wouldn't have had a problem
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.01,0:31:33.41,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Recently the number of people coming to see our performances has been decreasing
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.36,0:31:39.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Armed with just a microphone to determine victory and defeat for 20 to 30 years
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.76,0:31:43.15,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Kohori's heartfelt feelings are...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.05,0:31:51.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If only performing manzai was enough then i'd be very happy
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.26,0:31:53.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.66,0:31:59.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The reality is very different, I have four children and must rely on other jobs to support my family
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.80,0:32:02.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Honestly, that's it
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.11,0:32:09.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So...it's ready for today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.64,0:32:15.01,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,No... what do you think manzai is?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.98,0:32:20.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The reason why they won't give up manzai is...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.32,0:32:27.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The reason why I sometimes put them on the same stage with myself is
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.70,0:32:30.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They're kind of in a transitional state
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.13,0:32:34.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So I want to help give them the motivation to continue to work
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.60,0:32:38.51,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's like "I'll take the lead first"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.51,0:32:46.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Currently, his wife, Nonomura, who is active on television, is mainly responsible for the household
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.55,0:32:55.32,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Letting Nonomura work alone
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.32,0:32:56.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I think it is not a long-term solution
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.23,0:33:04.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What she wants to see the most is for me to achieve something in manzai
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.67,0:33:07.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So i'm am a bit anxious about this point
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.44,0:33:10.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't hate Kohori
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.87,0:33:13.94,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And I really like Nichokenju
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.31,0:33:17.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If there's less and less opportunities
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.21,0:33:20.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you can't get on TV
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.15,0:33:23.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Instead of becoming like that
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.82,0:33:28.89,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We should take advantage of the time when people still know and remember us
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.99,0:33:36.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Anything is fine, just do it, I think
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.70,0:33:41.44,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I really hope that in the New Year he won't be at home
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.44,0:33:43.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But instead, I can see Nichokenju on TV
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.77,0:33:49.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Do you have any goals for the future of Nichokenju?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.75,0:33:53.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After all, we started our manzai career once already, so we need to restart once again
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.18,0:33:56.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,We must rely on our manzai talent to conquer everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.79,0:34:01.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nichokenju's work is really interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.39,0:34:05.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But I think it's important to get the word out on the street
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.93,0:34:09.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The two of us just really love manzai
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.66,0:34:13.03,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,However, our talent alone hasn't led to popularity
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.03,0:34:15.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's been 29 years
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.47,0:34:18.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's right, right? You want to conquer everyone with your manzai talent, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.40,0:34:25.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A once iconic group come back to face the upcoming half-century
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.40,0:34:28.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With hope that one day their manzai talent will help them conquer
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.42,0:34:32.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please enjoy this song by Nichokenju
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.09,0:34:39.53,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)}Met you at NSC
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.48,0:34:38.86,note_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}※Yoshimoto's Academy for the Nurturing of Comedians
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.53,0:34:45.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With a playful outrageous attitude
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.87,0:34:53.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Bit the bullet and reluctantly became a combo
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.14,0:34:59.28,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And your scripts drew me into a vortex of laughter
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.28,0:35:06.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After a while, we were already a regular member of the "Super Alloy" team
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.28,0:35:06.29,note_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}※Yoshimoto Super Alloy popular variety show that aired from 1997 to 2000
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.29,0:35:11.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,450)}Double pistols with 100 rounds of laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.97,0:35:24.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)}Rode the wave to Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.07,0:35:29.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Pretentious and annoying
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.81,0:35:35.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The idiot neither making a sound nor playing dumb
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.92,0:35:42.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)} To be funny, "manzai is enough"
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.69,0:35:48.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I believed that one day I could get ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.23,0:35:55.30,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}However, the number of our performances is declining
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.60,0:35:57.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,By the 29th year
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.74,0:36:01.24,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I still think "these two people are really cool"
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.48,0:36:05.78,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Making people laugh brings happiness so I think it's a great job
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.38,0:36:09.65,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Nichokenju are really great
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.65,0:36:14.06,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I really hope I can keep watching them forever
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.06,0:36:15.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,In a large venue
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.52,0:36:20.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Where I can't believe so many people came to see Nichokenju
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.23,0:36:23.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I really want to create such a scene
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.27,0:36:31.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)}Rakugo and the band, don't be too enthusiastic
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.17,0:36:38.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,On the stage, two people standing side-by-side
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.58,0:36:46.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Don't stop writing
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.66,0:36:59.13,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,450)}Of course, I still love your words the most
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.60,0:37:04.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You really want to win an award?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.81,0:37:06.58,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.17,0:37:08.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Next is the last group
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.83,0:37:11.00,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Good morning
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.00,0:37:12.40,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Good morning
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.21,0:37:17.56,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,26 years' of experience: BlackPinnerSOS
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.15,0:37:21.92,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I've known them for a very long time
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.52,0:37:23.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.77,0:37:25.69,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I intend to support them from now on
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.69,0:37:26.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Starting now?  \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.70,0:37:27.60,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Starting now...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.60,0:37:30.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Its also fine not to
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.29,0:37:32.87,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Then why don't you just lie and say you're already supporting them?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.87,0:37:34.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,How dare you say such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.85,0:37:40.61,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The third group of struggling comedians are BlackPinnerSOS
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.30,0:37:48.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,26 years ago, a 16-year-old high school duo suddenly appeared
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.55,0:37:52.35,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Our live performances were very popular at Ota Production
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.35,0:37:56.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It was hard to even get a ticket
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.02,0:37:59.43,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"I called at the same time as the sale started but couldn't get through" or something like that
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.58,0:38:02.46,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And there were unimaginable amounts of screaming
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.46,0:38:07.27,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After the show, there were 20 to 30 people waiting outside
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.67,0:38:12.37,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Girls followed us all the way from the performance venue to the station
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.44,0:38:15.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,1 2 3 Black…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.04,0:38:20.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,With the advantage of youth and appearance
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.41,0:38:26.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,They flew head-first into the battlefield called "comedy"
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.59,0:38:31.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Really evil location
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.63,0:38:32.23,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.20,0:38:39.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Once VOCABULA ended
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.13,0:38:39.70,note_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}※VOCABULA Heavenly Kingdom - A super popular variety show hosted by Tamori from 1992 to 1999
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.70,0:38:45.74,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The number of programs featuring work like ours began to decrease
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.74,0:38:50.08,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Later on, it became impossible to muddle through with a lack of momentum
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.86,0:38:56.70,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After that, their high school student status disappeared and their popularity dropped
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.70,0:38:59.57,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And they faded into media obscurity
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.26,0:39:06.63,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The only weekly show left now is Mache Variety
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.26,0:39:06.63,note_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}※Live stream
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.63,0:39:08.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Is it a webcast? \N-Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.26,0:39:11.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Any work in theaters?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.97,0:39:17.21,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Performances are basically none now
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.92,0:39:20.96,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The two men are now 42 years old
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.98,0:39:23.86,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.86,0:39:26.50,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,You brought friends
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.50,0:39:28.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Yes, friends have come over
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.46,0:39:31.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Naito is the father of two sons
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.45,0:39:38.38,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,To protect his family
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.76,0:39:44.73,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I am a professional mahjong player
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.97,0:39:49.90,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Playing this game is my job
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.34,0:39:56.34,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I play four-player mahjong on the internet, and when I log in this comes up on the screen
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.34,0:39:59.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I play against players from all over the country
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.05,0:40:05.82,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, Aikata Yamano works part-time at an izakaya
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.82,0:40:10.66,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,At the same time he assists the running of his family's cosmetics store
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.19,0:40:18.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I'm also preparing to take the judicial exam
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.75,0:40:22.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,A lawyer comedian,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.47,0:40:24.67,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I don't know if there is a precedent, but it seems to be unheard of
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.07,0:40:27.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be a proper lawyer
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.11,0:40:30.76,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But if the party is absent I would be able to get involved, saying "I object" and so on
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.76,0:40:32.98,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although i'm not sure yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.18,0:40:35.68,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,"Caught vandalizing public property." "Caught and sentenced to how many years in prison."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.68,0:40:38.02,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although it is not very clear...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.02,0:40:43.26,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But I hope I can use it in some way to help our comedy progress
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.10,0:40:48.16,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The world of comedians clinging to their dream at all costs
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.53,0:40:55.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Although I am considered to be a comedian
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.77,0:41:01.88,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,But as i'm not so famous, when people ask, "What is your profession?" I can't answer "I'm a comedian"
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.88,0:41:04.45,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Our writing or whatever has never really been acknowledged
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.08,0:41:09.72,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Only we think we are comedians, but no one sees us as comedians
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.17,0:41:14.09,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you want to be a comedian...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.09,0:41:25.07,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,I hope that one day I will be able to say "I am a comedian" without hesitation
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.07,0:41:29.47,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After debuting at the age of 16, they fell back to earth after only four years
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.47,0:41:34.91,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After that, they continued to lurk for the next twenty years, living a hard life as comedians
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.91,0:41:37.81,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,So, please enjoy their song
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.15,0:41:45.39,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)}Met you in the first year of high school
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.39,0:41:52.29,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,The two weird guys in the same class
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.29,0:41:59.77,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Caught the attention of TV shows
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.77,0:42:06.97,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Became "high school stars" overnight
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.97,0:42:14.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Signed by Ota Productions and became a favorite on VOCABULA
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.75,0:42:21.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,450)}In the summer of 18 years old, the peak of life
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.53,0:42:34.84,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)}After taking off our uniforms, our value plummeted
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.84,0:42:42.04,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Abandoned by TV and banished by theaters
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.04,0:42:49.75,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Now humbly playing on the turf of newcomers
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.75,0:42:56.52,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,And lived a life of being teased by Miyashita Kusanagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.52,0:43:03.83,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Living a life of of part-time work
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.83,0:43:12.14,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,450)}In the spring of 42 years old, I lost my home
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.87,0:43:18.11,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Because of their age, there's no way to participate in competitions
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.45,0:43:24.25,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,It would be nice if he could inherit this store that I have worked so hard on
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.25,0:43:28.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,After all, it's not good to say you're an comedian at 42 years old
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.36,0:43:33.36,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,If you're a professional mahjong player, then people think you're the type of a person that can hold down their job
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.36,0:43:35.93,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That's what I say, but I always add a little note
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.93,0:43:38.80,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,That he's "also a comedian"
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.97,0:43:46.17,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)}Even if the family worry
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.17,0:43:52.85,normal_Wed,,0,0,0,,Please wait until I can be called an "comedian"
